I - Intelligent Documentation</title><meta name=\"description\" content=\"The AI-powered documentation engine that understands your codebase. Generate docs, audits, and diagrams in seconds.\"/><meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"DocuMint AI - Intelligent Documentation\"/><meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"The AI-powered documentation engine that understands your codebase.\"/><meta property=\"og:url\" content=\"https://documintai.dev\"/><meta property=\"og:site_name\" content=\"DocuMint AI\"/><meta property=\"og:locale\" content=\"en_US\"/><meta property=\"og:image\" content=\"https://documint-ai-master.vercel.app/og-image.png\"/><meta property=\"og:image:width\" content=\"1200\"/><meta property=\"og:image:height\" content=\"630\"/><meta property=\"og:image:alt\" content=\"DocuMint AI Preview\"/><meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"website\"/><meta name=\"twitter:card\" content=\"summary_large_image\"/><meta name=\"twitter:creator\" content=\"@documint_ai\"/><meta name=\"twitter:title\" content=\"DocuMint AI\"/><meta name=\"twitter:description\" content=\"The AI-powered documentation engine that understands your codebase.\"/><meta name=\"twitter:image\" content=\"https://documint-ai-master.vercel.app/og-image.png\"/><link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/favicon.ico?favicon.0b3bf435.ico\" sizes=\"256x256\" type=\"image/x-icon\"/><link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/favicon.ico\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/a6dad97d9634a72d.js\" noModule=\"\"></script></head><body class=\"geist_a71539c9-module__T19VSG__variable geist_mono_8d43a2aa-module__8Li5zG__variable antialiased\"><div hidden=\"\"><!--$--><!--/$--></div><div class=\"h-full\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(10px)\"><div class=\"min-h-screen bg-[#0A0A0B] text-white/80\"><header class=\"border-b border-white/5 bg-black/20 backdrop-blur-md sticky top-0 z-50\"><div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 h-16 flex items-center justify-between\"><a class=\"font-bold text-white tracking-tight flex items-center gap-2\" href=\"/\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-left w-4 h-4 text-muted-foreground\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m12 19-7-7 7-7\"></path><path d=\"M19 12H5\"></path></svg>DocuMint AI</a></div></header><main class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-12 prose prose-invert prose-headings:text-white prose-a:text-primary\"><div class=\"min-h-screen bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-900 to-slate-800 text-white\"><div class=\"container mx-auto px-4 py-16 max-w-4xl\"><div class=\"text-center mb-12\"><a class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-slate-300 hover:text-white transition-colors mb-6\" href=\"/\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-left w-4 h-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m12 19-7-7 7-7\"></path><path d=\"M19 12H5\"></path></svg>Back to Home</a><div class=\"flex items-center justify-center gap-3 mb-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-shield w-8 h-8 text-green-400\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z\"></path></svg><h1 class=\"text-4xl font-bold\">Privacy Policy</h1></div><p class=\"text-slate-400 text-lg\">Last updated: January 13, 2025</p></div><div class=\"bg-slate-800/50 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl p-8 space-y-8\"><section><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-green-400\">1. Introduction</h2><p class=\"text-slate-300 leading-relaxed\">At DocuMint AI, we take your privacy seriously. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you use our AI-powered code documentation generation service.</p><p class=\"text-slate-300 leading-relaxed mt-4\">By using DocuMint AI, you consent to the data practices described in this policy. If you do not agree with the terms of this Privacy Policy, please do not access the Service.</p></section><section><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-green-400\">2. Information We Collect</h2><div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6\"><div class=\"bg-slate-700/50 p-4 rounded-lg\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-3\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-mail w-5 h-5 text-blue-400\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m22 7-8.991 5.727a2 2 0 0 1-2.009 0L2 7\"></path><rect x=\"2\" y=\"4\" width=\"20\" height=\"16\" rx=\"2\"></rect></svg><h3 class=\"font-semibold\">Personal Information</h3></div><ul class=\"text-slate-300 space-y-2 text-sm\"><li>• Name and email address</li><li>• Account credentials</li><li>• Payment information (via Stripe)</li><li>• Profile information and preferences</li></ul></div><div class=\"bg-slate-700/50 p-4 rounded-lg\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-3\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-database w-5 h-5 text-purple-400\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><ellipse cx=\"12\" cy=\"5\" rx=\"9\" ry=\"3\"></ellipse><path d=\"M3 5V19A9 3 0 0 0 21 19V5\"></path><path d=\"M3 12A9 3 0 0 0 21 12\"></path></svg><h3 class=\"font-semibold\">Technical Information</h3></div><ul class=\"text-slate-300 space-y-2 text-sm\"><li>• IP address and browser information</li><li>• Device information and operating system</li><li>• Usage statistics and analytics</li><li>• Error logs and performance data</li></ul></div></div><div class=\"bg-slate-700/50 p-4 rounded-lg mt-4\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-3\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-eye-off w-5 h-5 text-red-400\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10.733 5.076a10.744 10.744 0 0 1 11.205 6.575 1 1 0 0 1 0 .696 10.747 10.747 0 0 1-1.444 2.49\"></path><path d=\"M14.084 14.158a3 3 0 0 1-4.242-4.242\"></path><path d=\"M17.479 17.499a10.75 10.75 0 0 1-15.417-5.151 1 1 0 0 1 0-.696 10.75 10.75 0 0 1 4.446-5.143\"></path><path d=\"m2 2 20 20\"></path></svg><h3 class=\"font-semibold\">Code Content</h3></div><p class=\"text-slate-300 text-sm\">We process the code you upload to generate documentation. This content is:</p><ul class=\"text-slate-300 space-y-1 text-sm mt-2\"><li>• Processed securely and temporarily</li><li>• Not stored permanently unless you save it</li><li>• Never shared with third parties</li><li>• Protected by strict access controls</li></ul></div></section><section><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-green-400\">3. How We Use Information</h2><div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6\"><div class=\"bg-slate-700/50 p-4 rounded-lg\"><h3 class=\"font-semibold mb-3 text-blue-400\">Service Operation</h3><ul class=\"text-slate-300 space-y-2 text-sm\"><li>• Provide and maintain the Service</li><li>• Process payments and subscriptions</li><li>• Authenticate users and secure accounts</li><li>• Send service-related communications</li></ul></div><div class=\"bg-slate-700/50 p-4 rounded-lg\"><h3 class=\"font-semibold mb-3 text-purple-400\">Service Improvement</h3><ul class=\"text-slate-300 space-y-2 text-sm\"><li>• Analyze usage patterns and trends</li><li>• Improve AI models and algorithms</li><li>• Fix bugs and optimize performance</li><li>• Develop new features</li></ul></div></div></section><section><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-green-400\">4. Data Sharing and Disclosure</h2><p class=\"text-slate-300 leading-relaxed\">We do not sell, trade, or rent your personal information to third parties. We may share information with:</p><ul class=\"text-slate-300 space-y-2 mt-3\"><li>• <strong>Service Providers:</strong> Trusted partners who help us operate our Service (payment processors, hosting providers)</li><li>• <strong>Legal Requirements:</strong> When required by law or to protect our rights</li><li>• <strong>Business Transfers:</strong> In connection with a merger or acquisition</li></ul><div class=\"bg-yellow-400/10 border border-yellow-400/20 rounded-lg p-4 mt-4\"><p class=\"text-yellow-300 text-sm\"><strong>Important:</strong> We use Stripe for payment processing. Your payment information is handled directly by Stripe and never touches our servers.</p></div></section><section><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-green-400\">5. Data Security</h2><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-lock w-6 h-6 text-green-400\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><rect width=\"18\" height=\"11\" x=\"3\" y=\"11\" rx=\"2\" ry=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4\"></path></svg><h3 class=\"font-semibold\">We Protect Your Data</h3></div><ul class=\"text-slate-300 space-y-3\"><li>• Encryption of data in transit and at rest</li><li>• Secure server infrastructure with regular updates</li><li>• Access controls and authentication mechanisms</li><li>• Regular security audits and monitoring</li><li>• Employee training on data protection</li></ul></section><section><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-green-400\">6. Your Rights</h2><p class=\"text-slate-300 leading-relaxed\">You have the right to:</p><ul class=\"text-slate-300 space-y-3 mt-3\"><li>• <strong>Access:</strong> Request a copy of your personal data</li><li>• <strong>Correction:</strong> Update or correct your information</li><li>• <strong>Deletion:</strong> Request deletion of your account and data</li><li>• <strong>Portability:</strong> Export your data in a portable format</li><li>• <strong>Restriction:</strong> Limit how we use your data</li></ul><p class=\"text-slate-400 text-sm mt-4\">To exercise these rights, please contact us at<!-- --> <a href=\"mailto:privacy@documint.ai\" class=\"text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300\">privacy@documint.ai</a></p></section><section><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-green-400\">7. Data Retention</h2><p class=\"text-slate-300 leading-relaxed\">We retain your personal information only for as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes outlined in this Privacy Policy, unless a longer retention period is required or permitted by law.</p><ul class=\"text-slate-300 space-y-2 mt-3\"><li>• Account data: Until account deletion</li><li>• Code content: Temporary processing, permanent if saved</li><li>• Payment records: As required by accounting laws</li><li>• Analytics data: Aggregated and anonymized</li></ul></section><section><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-green-400\">8. International Data Transfers</h2><p class=\"text-slate-300 leading-relaxed\">Your information may be processed in countries other than your own. We ensure appropriate safeguards are in place to protect your data in compliance with applicable data protection laws.</p></section><section><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-green-400\">9. Children&#x27;s Privacy</h2><p class=\"text-slate-300 leading-relaxed\">Our Service is not intended for individuals under the age of 18. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children. If you believe we have collected information from a child, please contact us immediately.</p></section><section><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-green-400\">10. Changes to This Policy</h2><p class=\"text-slate-300 leading-relaxed\">We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page and updating the &quot;Last updated&quot; date.</p></section><section><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-green-400\">11. Contact Us</h2><p class=\"text-slate-300 leading-relaxed\">If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us:</p><div class=\"mt-4 space-y-2\"><p class=\"text-slate-300\"><strong>Email:</strong> <a href=\"mailto:privacy@documint.ai\" class=\"text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300\">privacy@documint.ai</a></p><p class=\"text-slate-300\"><strong>Address:</strong> 123 Developer Street, Tech City, TC 12345</p></div></section></div><div class=\"text-center mt-12 text-slate-400\"><p>© <!-- -->2026<!-- --> DocuMint AI. All rights reserved.</p></div></div></div><!--$--><!--/$--></main><footer class=\"border-t border-white/5 py-12 mt-12\"><div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center text-sm text-muted-foreground\">© <!-- -->2026<!-- --> DocuMint AI. All rights reserved.</div></footer></div></div><!--$!--><template data-dgst=\"BAILOUT_TO_CLIENT_SIDE_RENDERING\"></template><!--/$--><div class=\"fixed bottom-4 right-4 z-50 flex flex-col gap-2\"></div><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/8e533c7b3b901b07.js\" id=\"_R_\" async=\"\"></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"1:\\\"$Sreact.fragment\\\"\\n2:I[1661,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/7f7dc44ea7af07e7.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/1f35f1e401cc8127.js\\\"],\\\"Providers\\\"]\\n3:I[232761,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/7f7dc44ea7af07e7.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/1f35f1e401cc8127.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n4:I[804277,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/7f7dc44ea7af07e7.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/1f35f1e401cc8127.js\\\"],\\\"PageTra